summary.label:
This application is a professional version of the free application AutoSender. It provides the following features,
- Obtain multiple in-app US and Canadian phone numbers for automatically or manually send text messages. Every US or Canadian number can receive unlimited text messages for free;
- Multiple attachments can be sent in one MMS;
- Provides professional-level in-app embedded eCard templates for MMS and SMS;
- Create and modify automatic messaging task based on the iOS native apps Calendar and Reminders content;
- Other features same as AutoSender app: Auto SMS/MMS sending, free SMS receiving (based on private number), auto SMS reply and auto SMS forwarding (based on private number), group messaging, etc.

This application provides an extremely low-cost and highly flexible solution for different application scenarios of individuals and SMEs:
- Subscribe to multiple USA or Canadian phone numbers (private numbers) within the app. With the private number(s) users can register multiple social network accounts, such as Apple ID, Facebook, WhatsApp, WeChat, Instagram, Twitter, Gmail, etc. . 
- Using one or more private numbers, users can send SMS or MMS messages anywhere in the world as if they are residents of the United States or Canada;
- Different phone numbers can be used to schedule marketing information automate sending at predefined time for specific channels. Different numbers can receive reply messages from different channels, which perfectly solves the problem of insufficient communication lines for small and medium-sized enterprises;
- Auto-reply, auto-reply-to-all and auto-forwarding on private numbers can be used for SMS Out-of-Office, customer service, SMS-based answering machines, etc.;
- All scheduled messaging tasks are executed automatically in the cloud. Suitable for mass messaging and telecommuting environments to automatically send text messages to your employees or partners, such as meeting notification, report submission, instructions, reminders, executions, etc.;
- For tenants to pay rent, employees to submit weekly/monthly reports, students to hand in assignments, etc. This is a reliable mass texting to be defined once and runs forever with enough credits;
- If you are in love with someone and want to send a romantic text or e-card to express your feelings over and over again, this will be the perfect tool to schedule love texts at the most heart-touching midnight moment;
- Scheduled event notifications, festival greetings, ceremony posters... all kind of pre-defined messages can utilize this tool for automated texting. 
- Shared Lines: By logging into multiple iOS devices with the same AutoSender (Pro) account, a group of people in different locations can use the same phone number as a phone line to communicate with the outside world - great for decentralized offices.

We also provide the Standard Subscriptions that offer extra services and features, priced from $0.99 monthly. Subscription automatically renews unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current period (30 days) and be charged to your iTunes account within 24-hours of the end of the current period, and identify the cost of the renewal. You can manage subscription and auto-renewal can be turned off by going to the user's Account Settings after purchase, but refunds will not be provided for any unused portion of the term.

Privacy Policy: https://www.freeramble.com/doc/FreeRamble_Privacy_Policy.html
Terms & Conditions: https://www.freeramble.com/doc/FreeRamble_Terms_Conditions.html

Note:
1) The alphabetical and numerical characters consume one byte per char, and other charset will consume more credits.
2) Only in USA & Canada contacts can receive MMS.
